title: Purple Sea Urchin
description: A vibrant purple sea urchin is resting on a rocky ocean floor, surrounded by colorful marine life and coral. The urchin's spiky exterior is prominently displayed against the blue background of the water.

title: Starfish on Rocks
description: A starfish with five arms, displaying a mix of purple and white colors, is resting on a bed of rocks and seaweed. The background features various textures of stones and marine vegetation, creating a natural coastal scene.

title: Colorful Sea Cucumber
description: A vibrant sea cucumber resting on the ocean floor, showcasing a mix of purple and orange colors with distinctive patterns. The surrounding sandy substrate is dotted with small marine plants and debris.

title: Sea Cucumber
description: A black sea cucumber with small white speckles, resting on a colorful underwater surface covered with algae and coral.

title: Purple Sea Urchin
description: A close-up view of a purple sea urchin, showcasing its vibrant purple color and long, sharp spines. The sea urchin is resting on a rocky surface, surrounded by marine life.

title: Orange Sea Star
description: An orange sea star with long, spiny arms is resting on a rocky surface covered in green algae. The sea star's texture is rough, and its arms are spread out, showcasing its unique features.

title: Close-up of a Sea Creature
description: A close-up image of a marine organism, possibly a type of sea cucumber or similar echinoderm. The creature has a segmented body covered in small, spiky protrusions and a pattern of orange and white coloration. The background is dark, highlighting the details of the creature's texture and form.
